{"tid":1759132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集中討論】三罷第一擊！！廣告界連續5天大罷工","createTime":"2019-11-27T12:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T15:16:46.000Z","uid":266540,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"470760d7d1701aff596fc6b986a0b8d70ca82543","tid":1759132,"uid":266540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:53:40.000Z","msg":"利申：自己都係廣告界agency<br />\n收到風 幾間agency都係要員工請假去罷工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔請假<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：請假<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我同我同事就係咪都罷既，五大訴求，缺一不可，未完架！！一個人罷工就無用，宜家全部人一齊陪你罷！所有廣告人唔該同我出哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHuECAX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHuECAX.png&h=faae2b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五天罷工，僅僅是「廣告公民」的起點。我們將會籌劃其他後續行動，如：推動黃色經濟圈，鼓勵業界為被捕人士提供就業機會等等，持續在自己的崗位上作戰。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，需眾同行；12.2罷工，不容再等。<br />\n<br />\n全員罷工：12月2日 &ndash; 6日<br />\n罷工集會：12月2日, 12-2PM，遮打花園 (不反對通知書申請中）<br />\n<br />\n*如有任何疑問，可參考FAQ: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/35aA3DK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35aA3DK&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=2818a88f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/35aA3DK</a><br />\n或發電郵到 advertisingpplhk@gmail.com"},{"pid":"60856000e6222b445bd6957b2943412e77b0bac0","tid":1759132,"uid":38837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"470760d7d1701aff596fc6b986a0b8d70ca82543","tid":1759132,"uid":266540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:53:40.000Z","msg":"利申：自己都係廣告界agency<br />\n收到風 幾間agency都係要員工請假去罷工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔請假<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"